<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>I Love You Kikuu ❤️</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
    overflow:hidden;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff4d6d,#ff758f,#ffb3c1);
    height:100vh;
}

/* Opening Screen */
#intro{
    position:fixed;
    inset:0;
    background:#000;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    flex-direction:column;
    z-index:999;
}

.heart{
    font-size:120px;
    animation:pulse 1.2s infinite;
}

.openText{
    color:white;
    margin-top:20px;
    font-size:24px;
}

@keyframes pulse{
    0%{transform:scale(1);}
    50%{transform:scale(1.3);}
    100%{transform:scale(1);}
}

#main{
    display:none;
    height:100vh;
    overflow:auto;
    text-align:center;
    color:white;
    padding:40px 20px;
}

h1{
    margin-top:80px;
    font-size:70px;
    font-family:'Dancing Script',cursive;
    text-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(255,255,255,.6);
}

.message{
    max-width:800px;
    margin:30px auto;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:20px;
    line-height:1.8;
    font-size:20px;
}

button{
    padding:15px 35px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:50px;
    background:white;
    color:#ff4d6d;
    font-size:18px;
    font-weight:bold;
    cursor:pointer;
    margin-top:20px;
}

.floating-heart{
    position:fixed;
    color:white;
    animation:float 10s linear infinite;
    opacity:.7;
}

@keyframes float{
    from{
        transform:translateY(100vh);
    }
    to{
        transform:translateY(-100px);
    }
}

.footer{
    margin-top:50px;
    font-size:24px;
    font-family:'Dancing Script',cursive;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div id="intro">
    <div class="heart">❤️</div>
    <div class="openText">For My Favourite Person...</div>
</div>

<div id="main">

<h1>I Love You Kikuu ❤️</h1>

<div class="message">

<p>
Ever since I met you, life has felt brighter, happier and more meaningful.
You came into my life when I didn't even realize how much I needed someone
like you.
</p>

<br>

<p>
Every conversation with you becomes my favourite part of the day.
Your smile can make a bad day feel beautiful, and your presence brings a
peace that words cannot fully describe.
</p>

<br>

<p>
It has been amazing since the day I met you. The memories we've created,
the laughs we've shared, and even the little moments together mean more to
me than you know.
</p>

<br>

<p>
You are not just special to me; you are the person who makes ordinary days
feel extraordinary. No matter where life takes us, I will always be grateful
for every moment spent with you.
</p>

<br>

<p>
Thank you for being yourself, for being kind, caring, beautiful and for
making my world a better place simply by being in it.
</p>

<br>

<p>
You will always have a very special place in my heart. ❤️
</p>

</div>

<button onclick="alert('Forever and Always ❤️')">
Forever & Always ❤️
</button>

<div class="footer">
Made with love, just for Kikuu ❤️
</div>

</div>

<script>

// Opening Animation
setTimeout(()=>{
    document.getElementById("intro").style.display="none";
    document.getElementById("main").style.display="block";
    document.body.style.overflow="auto";
},4000);

// Floating Hearts
for(let i=0;i<30;i++){
    let heart=document.createElement("div");
    heart.innerHTML="❤️";
    heart.classList.add("floating-heart");

    heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
    heart.style.fontSize=(Math.random()*25+15)+"px";
    heart.style.animationDuration=(Math.random()*8+5)+"s";

    document.body.appendChild(heart);
}

</script>

</body>
</html>
